h2-open-urls-from-paywalls-p2c300733.translation:
:::info
在 iOS SDK 中，`openUrl` 操作默认会触发打开 URL。但如有需要，您可以在代码中覆盖此行为。
:::

```swift
func paywallController(_ controller: AdaptyPaywallController,
                       didPerform action: AdaptyUI.Action) {
    switch action {
        case let .openURL(url):
            UIApplication.shared.open(url, options: [:]) // default behavior
        break
    }
}
```

h2-log-into-the-app-pe3b0c442.translation:
```swift
func paywallController(_ controller: AdaptyPaywallController,
                      didPerform action: AdaptyUI.Action) {
   switch action {
       case .login:
           // Show a login screen
           let loginVC = UIStoryboard(name: "Main", bundle: nil).instantiateViewController(withIdentifier: "LoginViewController")
           controller.present(loginVC, animated: true)
   }
}
```

